<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="he" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{subject}} - Help Savta</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset and base styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1f2937;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            direction: rtl;
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        /* Container */
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        /* Header */
        .email-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #1d4ed8 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .email-header h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .email-header .subtitle {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        /* Content */
        .email-content {
            padding: 32px 24px;
            direction: rtl;
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2563eb;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        
        .content-text {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            direction: rtl;
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        /* Info boxes */
        .info-box {
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            direction: rtl;
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        .info-box.success {
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            border-color: #22c55e;
            border-right: 4px solid #22c55e;
        }
        
        .info-box.warning {
            background-color: #fffbeb;
            border-color: #f59e0b;
            border-right: 4px solid #f59e0b;
        }
        
        .info-box.info {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            border-color: #3b82f6;
            border-right: 4px solid #3b82f6;
        }
        
        .info-box h3 {
            color: #1f2937;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        
        .info-box.success h3 {
            color: #15803d;
        }
        
        .info-box.warning h3 {
            color: #d97706;
        }
        
        .info-box.info h3 {
            color: #1d4ed8;
        }
        
        /* Request details */
        .request-details {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            direction: rtl;
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #1f2937;
            text-align: right;
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        /* Urgency badges */
        .urgency-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .urgency-low {
            background-color: #dcfce7;
            color: #166534;
        }
        
        .urgency-medium {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            color: #92400e;
        }
        
        .urgency-high {
            background-color: #fed7d7;
            color: #c53030;
        }
        
        .urgency-urgent {
            background-color: #fee2e2;
            color: #dc2626;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.8; }
        }
        
        /* Status badges */
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .status-pending {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            color: #92400e;
        }
        
        .status-in_progress {
            background-color: #dbeafe;
            color: #1e40af;
        }
        
        .status-completed {
            background-color: #dcfce7;
            color: #166534;
        }
        
        /* Action buttons */
        .action-buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 8px;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #1d4ed8;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: #6b7280;
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #4b5563;
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer-text {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #6b7280;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 16px;
            padding-top: 16px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .contact-info strong {
            color: #374151;
        }
        
        /* Responsive design */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .email-container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .email-content {
                padding: 20px 16px;
            }
            
            .email-header {
                padding: 20px 16px;
            }
            
            .email-header h1 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 4px;
            }
            
            .detail-label {
                min-width: auto;
            }
            
            .detail-value {
                text-align: right;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Help Savta</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">עזרה טכנית בהתנדבות לקהילה</div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="email-content">
            {{{content}}}
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="email-footer">
            <div class="footer-text">
                <strong>צוות Help Savta</strong><br>
                שירות עזרה טכנית בהתנדבות לקהילה
            </div>
            
            {{#if supportEmail}}
            <div class="contact-info">
                <strong>ליצירת קשר:</strong><br>
                📧 {{supportEmail}}<br>
                {{#if supportPhone}}📞 {{supportPhone}}{{/if}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="footer-text" style="margin-top: 16px; font-size: 11px;">
                אימייל זה נשלח אוטומטית ממערכת Help Savta.<br>
                אנא אל תשיבו ישירות לאימייל זה.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>